'''Charlie Sophonpanich''' , ({{zh|c=<U+9673><U+667A><U+6DE6>}}) is second son of [[Chatri Sophonpanich]], grandson of [[Chin Sophonpanich]]. And he serves as the [[President]] of [[Asia Investment]]. [[Bangkok Bank]] is his family business.

